      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in such incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the lot! It drives like a dream and has been pampered every single mile. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a new home, this is the one. Come check it out, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
