      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 inline-six with its factory-spec individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS system functioning flawlessly. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and recently serviced rod bearings, ensuring mechanical integrity remains uncompromising. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry remains true to factory specs, utilizing fresh bushings and dampers for signature M-division tactile response. A turn-key specimen for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
