      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade specimen that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior paint finish that retains its original factory depth and a mirror-like luster, free of any swirl marks or stone chips. The cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple and matte, lacking any bolster wear, while the high-gloss interior trim is devoid of micro-scratches. Every switch operates with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, featuring a spotless engine bay and a comprehensive service portfolio documented exclusively by authorized technicians. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched spare tire well, this car offers a 'new-old-stock' driving experience that is impossible to replicate. It remains 100% original, accident-free, and ready for the show lawn.",
